column44:
I've known my wife, Suzukari, since we
were kids. Even then she was a darling;
it was love at first sight for me.

column48:
Conozco a Suzukari, mi mujer, desde que
éramos niños. Ya entonces era adorable;
me enamoré de ella en cuanto la vi.

